    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "MIDWAY AIRLINES\nTIMETABLE\nEffective December 1, 1990\nMidway Airlines\nIncluding\nMidway Connection\nFor reservations, call\n(800) 866-9000",
      "HARTFORD/SPRINGFIELD\nMidway Airlines®\nproudly introduces\nnon-stop service between\nHartford/Springfield\nand Chicago\nbeginning January 8, 1991.\nSERV\nWith four daily round-trips, the only\nnon-stop service between Bradley\nInternational and Chicago's\nconvenient Midway Airport.\nMidway Airlines®\n~ FLYERSFIRST.\nFlyersFirst® members earn\ndouble flight credits on this new\nroute between January 8 and\nMarch 31, 1991.\n© Midway Airlines, 1990."
    ],
